oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: LeFevres at a Mid-night Gospel Sing at the Newman Municipal Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Gospel music; Martha White Foods; LeFevres;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing an Midnight Gospel Sing with the LeFevres, Little Troy Lumpkin and the Messengers Quartet at the Municipal Auditorium on March 19. Poster features metal photoplates of the LeFevres.
